      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected on the basis of prior literature without systematic comparison to alternative turbulence closures (e.g., RSM, LES) for rotating hemolysis applications. Power-law hemolysis model (Giersiepen-Wurzinger) not compared to alternative formulations. Model form uncertainty not quantified. Flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5."
